# --- Data & derived artifacts (large; reproducible, not versioned) ---
# Keep raw downloads and derived marts out of git; see README "Repository / data-mart layout".
# Ignore data/ CONTENTS (not the dir itself) so specific subdirs can be re-included below.
data/*
# ...but do track small, reproducibility-critical manifests and frozen splits.
!data/manifests/
!data/splits/

